handoff\:"Skip the chat loop and spawn the agent CLI interactively for every \`how = "ai"\` file. kata stops re-importing"))' \
'--ai-concurrency=[Maximum concurrent AI calls (chat turns / handoff spawns / editor round-trips). Overrides \`defaults.ai_concurrency\` (default 4) for this run]:N:_default' \
