':preset -- Preset spec\: `<source>\[@<rev>\]\[//<subdir>\]\[\:<preset-name>\]`. `<source>` is a git URL (e.g. `github.com/owner/repo`) or a local path; `<preset-name>` defaults to `default`:_default' \
&& ret=0
;;
(apply)
_arguments "${_arguments_options[@]}" : \
'--at=[Project root (defaults to cwd, walking upwards to find \`.kata/applied.toml\`)]:DIR:_default' \
